title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Myers/Russo/Fletcher/Leopold
description: Vox In The Box is back! Wild.com's Dan Myers (1-0) co-hosts for the first hour, which features Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau. Michael Russo from The Athletic talks trade deadline and more. Wild GM Chuck Fletcher shares his thoughts on Monday morning's happenings and Jordan Leopold closes out the program talking about how difficult it can be, logistically, to be traded.
